OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774001116
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Labour should pledge to
OL,4,Crejoin the EU at next election
OL,6,FRejoining the European Union should be
OL,7,Fa Labour pledge at the next general
OL,8,Felection, the Mayor of London has
OL,9,Fargued.
OL,11,FSpeaking to Italian newspaper La
OL,12,FRepubblica, Sir Sadiq Khan set out a
OL,13,Froad map for closer ties with the EU,
OL,14,Fincluding rejoining both the customs
OL,15,Funion and the single market.
OL,17,F"I see on a daily basis the damage
OL,18,FBrexit has done to not just London,
OL,19,Fbut to Londoners, the damage
OL,20,Feconomically, socially and
OL,21,Fculturally," he said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU}D@LO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
