OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774001116
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Labour should pledge to
OL,4,Crejoin the EU at next election
OL,6,F"I'm quite clear in terms of what
OL,7,Fneeds to happen, which is, we should
OL,8,Fjoin the European Union."
OL,10,FSir Sadiq pointed to the election of
OL,11,FUS President Donald Trump, growing
OL,12,Fglobal instability and the passage of
OL,13,Ftime as reasons to revisit the issue,
OL,14,Farguing that "the facts have changed"
OL,15,Fand "the evidence has changed".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@YO]vD@NOUvD@eO]wD@EOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
