CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774001116
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Labour should pledge to
OL,4,Crejoin the EU at next election
OL,6,F"We should, as a Labour Party, fight
OL,7,Fthe next general election with a clear
OL,8,Fmanifesto commitment, a vote for
OL,9,FLabour means we would rejoin the
OL,10,FEuropean Union. I think it's
OL,11,Finevitable," he said.
OL,13,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,14,Fsought to "reset" relations with
OL,15,FBrussels in an effort to improve trade
OL,16,Fties since his election in 2024.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@LO]vD@KOUvD@QO]
