OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774001116
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Labour should pledge to
OL,4,Crejoin the EU at next election
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves earlier this
OL,7,Fweek warned the UK risked being
OL,8,F"stranded" between rival trading blocs
OL,9,Funless it forged closer ties with
OL,10,FBrussels.
OL,12,FShe said any divergence from EU
OL,13,Fregulations would be limited,
OL,14,Fdescribing it as "the exception, not
OL,15,Fthe norm".
OL,17,FMs Reeves added: "Our fate as a
OL,18,Fcountry is inescapably bound with that
OL,19,Fof Europe."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@JO]vD@ROUwD@IO]yD@ROU{D@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
