CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774001116
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Labour should pledge to
OL,4,Crejoin the EU at next election
OL,6,FBy the time of the next joint summit
OL,7,Flater this year, the UK and EU want to
OL,8,Ffinalise agreements on a youth
OL,9,Fmobility scheme, as well as
OL,10,Festablishing a common sanitary and
OL,11,Fphytosanitary area and on linking
OL,12,Ftheir emissions trading systems.
OL,14,FIn February, Downing Street dismissed
OL,15,Fthe prospect of rejoining the customs
OL,16,Funion after European economic
OL,17,Fcommissioner Valdis Dombrovskis said
OL,18,Fthe bloc would be open to discussions.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
