PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774001116
OL,3,CSadiq Khan: Labour should pledge to
OL,4,Crejoin the EU at next election
OL,6,F"We do want a closer economic
OL,7,Fpartnership with the EU, but rejoining
OL,8,Fthe customs union would unpick
OL,9,Fimportant trade agreements we've
OL,10,Freached, including our deals with the
OL,11,FUS and India."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
